---
title: Cherry Tomato, Bacon & Sage Pizza with Pear & Mixed Leaf Salad
description: Add extra flavour to your pizza by roasting the veggies first to ensure every bite is a tasty delight. Then, infuse the
sauce with garlic for a fragrant flavour so divine that you’ll never rely on takeaway again!

